file: tmp_【３D】ライブも企画も！誕生日祭だーー！！！！【 #大神ミオ誕生日 】 [ChMwx4yeI3g]_gemini-3-flash-preview/reencoded/part_009.mov

scenes.description: Ookami Mio, Oozora Subaru, and Nekomata Okayu finish a segment and chat in the office set before the guests leave to find cake.
Tokoyami Towa arrives at the office on her day off and decides to perform a song with Mio.
Mio and Towa appear on the idol stage and introduce their next song.

subtitles.original: ミミミミミミッミッミ...
subtitles.english: Mi mi mi mi mi mi mi...

subtitles.original: これが楽しいんだよ！
subtitles.english: This is what's fun!

subtitles.original: やたら楽しそうだった。
subtitles.english: You seemed to be having an awful lot of fun.

subtitles.original: カメラさんもちゃんと拾ってくれてたし。
subtitles.english: The cameraman was capturing it perfectly, too.

subtitles.original: でもカメラさん「どっちが振り向くんだ！？」ってなったでしょ。
subtitles.english:
But the cameraman must've been like,
"Which one's gonna turn around!?"

subtitles.original: どっちかな？
subtitles.english: Which one?

subtitles.original: こっちか？
subtitles.english: This one?

subtitles.original: 確かに確かに。
subtitles.english: True, true.

subtitles.original: あー楽しかったね。
subtitles.english: Ah, that was fun.

subtitles.original: やり切ったわ。
subtitles.english: We gave it our all.

subtitles.original: ていうかさ、ころさんは？
subtitles.english: By the way, where's Koro-san?

subtitles.original: あ、あれ？ころさん帰って来なくない？
subtitles.english: Oh, wait. Isn't Koro-san coming back?

subtitles.original: え、じゃあケーキは？
subtitles.english: Eh? Then what about the cake?

subtitles.original: あ、もう食べてるかもしれないからさ。
subtitles.english: Ah, she might be eating it already.

subtitles.original: 僕たち先に探しておくよ。
subtitles.english: We'll go look for it ahead of you.

subtitles.original: え、うちの誕生日ケーキ...
subtitles.english: Wait, my birthday cake...

subtitles.original: じゃあ！
subtitles.english: See ya!

subtitles.original: ミオちゃん、ミオちゃん、ここにまだいなさいよ。
subtitles.english: Mio-chan, Mio-chan, you stay here for now.

subtitles.original: 分かった？準備があるでしょう？うちらのライブのね。
subtitles.english: Got it? You have prep to do, right? For our live show.

subtitles.original: じゃ、スバルたちは一足先にケーキにありつくぜ！
subtitles.english:
Well, Subaru and the others are gonna
go get that cake first!

subtitles.original: 待ってよ！ケーキ！
subtitles.english: Wait! Cake!

subtitles.original: うちのケーキなのに...
subtitles.english: Even though it's my cake...

subtitles.original: いなくなっちゃった。
subtitles.english: They're gone.

subtitles.original: でも二人とも、ありがとう！
subtitles.english: But thanks to both of you!

subtitles.original: じゃ、うちはちょっとゆっくりするか。
subtitles.english: Well, I guess I'll relax for a bit.

subtitles.original: ウッキー！ミオしゃーん！
subtitles.english: Uuuki! Mio-shaan!

subtitles.original: よーうしゃ！事務所だってばー！
subtitles.english: Yo-sha! I'm telling you, it's the office!

subtitles.original: ミオしゃーん！
subtitles.english: Mio-shaan!

subtitles.original: なんだなんだ、何そのテンション。
subtitles.english: What's going on? What's with that energy?

subtitles.original: なんかちょっとテンションおかしくない？大丈夫？
subtitles.english: Your energy is a bit weird, isn't it? Are you okay?

subtitles.original: 今日は、今日はなんと...
subtitles.english: Today... Today is actually...

subtitles.original: お休みの日だけど... イェイイェイイェイ！
subtitles.english: My day off, but... Yay yay yay!

subtitles.original: なんか誰かいるかなーと思って来ちゃったわけよ。
subtitles.english: I thought someone might be here, so I stopped by.

subtitles.original: 遊びに来たってこと？
subtitles.english: You mean you came to play?

subtitles.original: そうそうそう。
subtitles.english: Yeah, yeah, yeah.

subtitles.original: なんで事務所なのにアイドル衣装なの？
subtitles.english: Why are you in an idol outfit even though we're in the office?

subtitles.original: ああ、ま、ちょっといろいろ海より深い理由が...
subtitles.english: Ah, well, for various reasons deeper than the ocean...

subtitles.original: 海より深いの！？
subtitles.english: Deeper than the ocean!?

subtitles.original: 山より高いってこと？
subtitles.english: You mean higher than the mountains?

subtitles.original: まあまあまあ、そういうことかな。
subtitles.english: Well, well, I guess it's something like that.

subtitles.original: え、何してたの？
subtitles.english: Eh, what were you doing?

subtitles.original: えっ、もうあのね、歌ったりとかしてたんだけどさ。
subtitles.english: Eh, well, I was doing things like singing.

subtitles.original: ここで？
subtitles.english: In here?

subtitles.original: まあまあまあ、そうだね。
subtitles.english: Well, yeah.

subtitles.original: この格好で？
subtitles.english: In that outfit?

subtitles.original: この格好で。
subtitles.english: In this outfit.

subtitles.original: うわー、すごいね。
subtitles.english: Whoa, that's amazing.

subtitles.original: なんか「歌え」って言われて。
subtitles.english: I was told to "sing."

subtitles.original: あ、歌えって言われたの？
subtitles.english: Oh, you were told to sing?

subtitles.original: え、トワもミオちゃんと歌いたい！
subtitles.english: Eh, Towa wants to sing with Mio-chan too!

subtitles.original: え、歌ってくれるの？
subtitles.english: Eh, you'll sing with me?

subtitles.original: これ誕生日ライブなんだけど大丈夫？
subtitles.english: This is a birthday live, though. Is that okay?

subtitles.original: あ、じゃあちょっと恥ずかしいからやめとく。
subtitles.english: Ah, then I'm a bit embarrassed, so I'll pass.

subtitles.original: なんでやねん！
subtitles.english: Why not!?

subtitles.original: 突然やめんな。
subtitles.english: Don't suddenly quit on me.

subtitles.original: え、ええの？誕生日なのに。
subtitles.english: Eh, is it okay? Even though it's my birthday.

subtitles.original: トワが出しゃばっていい、みんな？
subtitles.english: Is it okay for Towa to barge in, everyone?

subtitles.original: イェーイ！歌ってほしい？イェーイ！
subtitles.english: Yay! Do you want us to sing? Yay!

subtitles.original: じゃあ、せっかくだからトワもアイドル衣装きちゃう？
subtitles.english:
Then, since we're at it, why don't you
put on an idol outfit too, Towa?

subtitles.original: え... やっぱ着るのやめようかな。
subtitles.english: Eh... maybe I'll pass on wearing it after all.

subtitles.original: なんでやねん！
subtitles.english: Why not!?

subtitles.original: 嘘、着たい！着たい着たい！
subtitles.english: Just kidding, I want to! I want to, I want to!

subtitles.original: 着たいね。じゃあちょっとアイドル衣装ついでにステージも変えちゃおうかな。
subtitles.english:
You want to, right. Then since we're changing outfits,
let's change the stage too.

subtitles.original: お、変えよう変えよう変えよう！
subtitles.english: Oh, let's change it, let's change it!

subtitles.original: せーの、どん！
subtitles.english: One, two, jump!

subtitles.original: 来ましたよー！
subtitles.english: We're here!

subtitles.original: 来たぜー！イェーイ！
subtitles.english: We've arrived! Yay!

subtitles.original: というわけでね、可愛い衣装に着替えたところでね。
subtitles.english: And so, now that we've changed into cute outfits.

subtitles.original: 緊張してきた！
subtitles.english: I'm getting nervous!

subtitles.original: 緊張してきた？
subtitles.english: You're getting nervous?

subtitles.original: 何歌うか知ってる？
subtitles.english: Do you know what we're going to sing?

subtitles.original: 知ってるよ。
subtitles.english: I know.

subtitles.original: 知ってた。
subtitles.english: I knew it.

subtitles.original: テレパシーで通じちゃった。
subtitles.english: We connected via telepathy.

subtitles.original: なんだその間は。
subtitles.english: What was with that pause?

subtitles.original: ちょっとあのいい感じの大人の魅力を出してみた。
subtitles.english: I was trying to project some of that 'adult charm.'

subtitles.original: あ、そういうこと？大人の魅力じゃあちょっと頑張って追求していく歌なのかな？
subtitles.english:
Ah, is that it? So is it a song where we have
to work on our adult charm?

subtitles.original: 分かんないけど。
subtitles.english: I don't know though.

subtitles.original: いや、ちゃうわ。
subtitles.english: No, that's not it.

subtitles.original: 違うかい！
subtitles.english: It's not!?

subtitles.original: ちょっとあのハッピーな感じで行くかな。
subtitles.english: I think we'll go with a happy vibe.

subtitles.original: ハッピーな感じでね。イェーイイェーイ！じゃあみんな盛り上がっていきましょう！
subtitles.english:
With a happy vibe, right. Yay yay!
Then everyone, let's get hyped!

subtitles.original: というわけで、次で二人で歌う曲いっちゃいましょうか！
subtitles.english: So, let's go with the next song we'll sing together!

subtitles.original: おい！
subtitles.english: Hey!

subtitles.original: せーの！BLUE CLAPPER！
subtitles.english: One, two! BLUE CLAPPER!

subtitles.original: 手を上げて Clap your hands / 生み出す航路まで Clap your hands
subtitles.english:
Raise your hands and clap your hands /
To the course that we create, clap your hands

subtitles.original: 届きますように
subtitles.english: I hope it reaches you

subtitles.original: 手を叩こう 手を叩こう ほら一緒に
subtitles.english:
Let's clap our hands, let's clap our hands,
come on, together

subtitles.original: Everybody Clap your hands / 空に響く方まで Clap your hands
subtitles.english:
Everybody clap your hands /
Until it reaches the sky, clap your hands

subtitles.original: 響きますように
subtitles.english: I hope it resonates

subtitles.original: 手を叩こう 手を叩こう
subtitles.english: Let's clap our hands, let's clap our hands

subtitles.original: 光射す僕たちの未来
subtitles.english: The light shines on our future

subtitles.original: Hi! Ho! 4
subtitles.english: High! Ho! 4

subtitles.original: 1 トワ様降臨！
subtitles.english: 1 Towa-sama has arrived!

subtitles.original: 始めようか Get ready 待っても意味ないタイミング
subtitles.english:
Shall we begin? Get ready,
there's no point in waiting for the timing

subtitles.original: あの魚みたいに Swimming swimming
subtitles.english: Like that fish, swimming swimming

subtitles.original: 引き寄せる Lighting まだ見えない
subtitles.english: Drawing in the lighting, still can't see it
